Aflac Inc. (AFL) , the largest seller of
supplemental health insurance, said it hired Julia K. Davis as
senior vice president and chief information officer.  Davis is a former chief information officer at  American
Safety Insurance Holdings Ltd. (ASI) , Columbus, Georgia-based Aflac
said today in a statement distributed by PR Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
